<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4779389>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figs 11-22: Colour pattern of left elytron. – 11-16: Exomala campestris – 17-22: Exomala succincta – 11-13, 17-19: . – 14-16, 20-22: . – 11, 14, 17, 20: Specimens with reduced dark marks. – 12, 15, 18, 21: Specimens with moderately developed dark marks. – 13, 16, 19, 22: Specimens with well developed dark marks. – 11: Gallia mer. – 12: France. – 13: Gironde: La Teste. – 14: France. – 15: France. – 16:Wironde: Soulac-sur-Mer.– 17: Tirol. – 18:Tirol mer. – 19: Tirol. – 20: Emilia, Reno. – 21: Piemonte: Garearel. – 22: Bolzano." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4779389/files/figure.png" .

